title: War of the Roses: Wax On or Wax Off?
description: McKayla has been casually dating Jeremy and doesn't know if he's seeing just her or other people.  She has a a wax appointment and doesn't want to waste it on Jeremy if they're aren't exclusive.  So she wants to do a little War of the Roses to get her answer.
